INTRODUCTION
============
MusicFS provides an FUSE-Filesystem that is build from ID3-Tags with different categories.

REQUIREMENTS
=============
- Perl 5.10
- Perl Module Fuse
- Perl module MP3::Tag
- Fuse

USAGE
=====
perl musicfs.pl <basedir> <moutpoint>

<basedir> - where your audiofiles are located (will readed recursive)
<mountpoint> - where to mount the musicfs

KNOWN ISSUES/LIMITATIONS
========================
- only MPEG1 Layer3-Audiofiles are readed
- The MP3-Files need to have an IDv1 Tag. IDv2 is not supported yet.

